OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FA man who shot a father dead in a case
OL,7,Fof mistaken identity has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor life.
OL,10,FDale Stogden was walking along
OL,11,FDoncaster Road in Wakefield when he
OL,12,Fwas shot by Leyton Davies from a
OL,13,Fpassing car in August last year.
OL,15,FThe 50-year-old, known as Brett, was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital where he died of his
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
