FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FDavies, 28, became the third person to
OL,7,Fbe jailed for killing Mr Stogden on
OL,8,FFriday, joining 21-year-old Adam Ahmed
OL,9,Fand 20-year-old Marc Carter who were
OL,10,Fboth sentenced to 12 years in March.
OL,12,FPolice said at the time they believed
OL,13,Fthe three had intended to target two
OL,14,Fother men who had been in the vicinity
OL,15,Fat the time, and were witnessed
OL,16,Frunning away immediately after the
OL,17,Ffatal shot was fired.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FCCTV had shown the three killers
OL,7,Fdriving around the area on the day of
OL,8,Fthe shooting, while messages exchanged
OL,9,Fbetween them and a fourth man - who
OL,10,Fwas not in the car at the time -
OL,11,Findicated they had been searching for
OL,12,Fthe other two who were seen fleeing
OL,13,Fthe scene.
OL,15,FThe RAV4 used to carry out the
OL,16,Fshooting had been reported stolen in
OL,17,Fnearby Castleford and given cloned
OL,18,Fplates when Davies, Ahmed and Carter
OL,19,Fgot in it on the evening of August 12
OL,20,Fand began prowling the area.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FAhmed was driving, with Carter in the
OL,7,Fpassenger seat and Davies sitting
OL,8,Fbehind, bearing the weapon - believed
OL,9,Fto be a converted blank firing pistol
OL,10,Fwhich has never been recovered.
OL,12,FAhmed had also been seen on CCTV
OL,13,Fcarrying a machete shortly before the
OL,14,Fshooting.
OL,16,FAll three were convicted at Leeds
OL,17,FCrown Court of manslaughter in March,
OL,18,Fhaving already pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fsupplying Class A drugs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
