PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FDavies was jailed for life on Friday
OL,7,Fwith a minimum of 33 years for his
OL,8,Fpart in killing Mr Stogden.
OL,10,FMr Stogden's family said in a
OL,11,Fstatement following the sentencing
OL,12,Fthat no sentence would "ever be good
OL,13,Fenough in our eyes", but that the jail
OL,14,Fterm handed to Davies on Friday gave
OL,15,F"at least a little bit of closure".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
