PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp James Entwistle, of West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police's Homicide and Major
OL,8,FEnquiry Team, said: "Today's
OL,9,Fsentencing marks the final chapter in
OL,10,Fthe court proceedings, and I hope it
OL,11,Fhelps those who knew and loved Brett
OL,12,Fas they continue to move forward with
OL,13,Ftheir own lives.
OL,15,F"I also hope that the wider public are
OL,16,Freassured that the three men
OL,17,Fresponsible for Brett's death are now
OL,18,Fall serving jail terms.
OL,26,@pD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779041473
OL,3,CDrive-by shooter who killed dad in
OL,4,Ccase of mistaken identity jailed
OL,6,F"We will not tolerate the use of
OL,7,Ffirearms, with this case showing the
OL,8,Fabsolutely devastating impact that
OL,9,Fjust one shot can have.
OL,11,F"The weapon used in this shooting was
OL,12,Fa blank firing firearm which had been
OL,13,Fillegally converted. We will continue
OL,14,Fto work to take weapons such as these
OL,15,Fout of the hands of criminals."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
